      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:5:3:33:4",
      "text": [
        " لَا يَتَزَوَّجُ الْيَهُودِيَّةَ وَ لَا النَّصْرَانِيَّةَ عَلَى الْمُسْلِمَةِ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Muhammad Bin Yahy, from Ahmad Bin Muhammad, from Ali Bin Al Hakam, from Al A’ala Bin Razeyn, from Muhammad Bin Muslim, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Ja’far<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘Do not marry the Jewish woman, nor the Christian woman upon (as additional wife) the Muslim woman’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "4. Muhammad ibn Yahya has narrated from Ahmad ibn Muhammad from Ali ibn al-Hakam from al-‘Ala’ ibn Razin from Muhammad ibn Muslim who has said the following: “Abu Ja‘far, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘A Jewish or a Christian woman cannot become a second wife, the first being a Muslim woman.’” "
        ]
      }
    },
